{"tid":1455243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場有班恐怖份子係完美劇本","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:39.000Z","uid":282414,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb1b8bc5fc160ee74a93e8ed63bc2415955a3348","tid":1455243,"uid":282414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:48:55.000Z","msg":"今日下午四點，國務院突然開記者招待會，談論香港情況，竟然話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">恐怖主義開始苗頭</span>。<br />\n你可能會話靠嚇呀? 邊忽恐怖主義? <br />\n但共產黨自然會<span style=\"color: red;\">弄假成真</span>。<br />\n機場正正係恐怖份子最中意攻擊的地方。<br />\n宜家只有抵港班機，唔同的工作人員都要early release，好多人都影到有狗扮抗爭者，防暴已經大舉入場。<br />\n當無咩旅客，機場得返警察和抗爭者，你話會唔會出現衝突? 會唔會有「抗爭者」收唔住挑釁行為過激? <br />\n<br />\n我希望所有嘢都係巧合，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">空穴來風，小心請君入甕</span></span></strong>。"},{"pid":"c4d78647e9c6353ff3901bc8c36d5f6beb9543ee","tid":1455243,"uid":75959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:51:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">未封自己決定去留，封左橋大家記住旅客安全要緊，去T2 保護佢地</span></span>"},{"pid":"8fbf885a1b8d2b36499f2415832b79d2b8b977f9","tid":1455243,"uid":282414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4d78647e9c6353ff3901bc8c36d5f6beb9543ee","tid":1455243,"uid":75959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:51:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">未封自己決定去留，封左橋大家記住旅客安全要緊，去T2 保護佢地</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"我純講出個人擔心，我見到大家一車車去機場有種集中營的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n可能我太受琴日影響。"},{"pid":"2c0c2e3bef94d915886cf64bb8e360c7cef84976","tid":1455243,"uid":288486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"89bf76e13ab4fcdf0784aeb9d133890da03891ae","tid":1455243,"uid":89197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"去機場係想向旅客宣傳，依家無旅客，班狗又佈晒防，Be Water 啦"},{"pid":"921357aafa7183b5